On Friday, December 2nd, 2016 Danielle Stislicki was last seen leaving her place of work. Her family quickly became aware that Danielle was missing. Farmington Hills police were alerted and immediately they began searching for Danielle. Very quickly, police were able to determine that Danielle was the victim of foul play.
